      • importBookingHistory

        public static java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.util.List<java.lang.String>> importBookingHistory(User user)
                                                                                             throws org.json.JSONException,
                                                                                                    java.io.IOException
        Gets the full booking history of the Customer from the database. The history is stored inside a HashMap, so that specific bookings can be accessed using keys.
        Parameters:
        user - the Customer whose booking is to be imported.
        Returns:
        the booking history of the Customer.
        Throws:
        org.json.JSONException - if the JSON object cannot be found.
        java.io.IOException - if the file cannot be found.
